TITLE: Configuring ElectroDB Entity for Mall Store Directory
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript code defines an ElectroDB Entity named 'StoreLocations' for a mall store directory service. It specifies the model, attributes, and indexes for the entity, including validation rules and composite keys for different access patterns.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tywalch/electrodb/blob/master/www/src/partials/entity-query-example-setup.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import DynamoDB from "aws-sdk/clients/dynamodb";
import { Entity } from "electrodb";

