SOURCE: https://github.com/tywalch/electrodb/blob/master/www/src/pages/en/examples/library-system.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_24

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
await genre.query
  .author({ authorFirstName: "stephen", authorLastName: "king" })
  .go()
  .then((results) => {
