TITLE: Adding New Language Support in Astro Config
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to add Spanish as a supported language by updating the KNOWN_LANGUAGES map in the config.ts file to enable the language switcher in the site header.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tywalch/electrodb/blob/master/www/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: diff
CODE:
```
// src/config.ts
export const KNOWN_LANGUAGES = {
  English: 'en',
+  Spanish: 'es',
};
```

