TITLE: Changing Default Language Redirect
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to modify the default language redirect in the index.astro file to use Spanish as the default language instead of English.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tywalch/electrodb/blob/master/www/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: diff
CODE:
```
